How to Play Number Position

1. Signing Up

To start playing, you need to create an account. Click on the "Sign Up" button on the homepage and fill in your details.

2. Logging In

Once you have an account, log in using your email and password. Click on the "Log In" button on the homepage.

3. Logging Out

To log out, click on the "Logout" button located in the navigation bar.

4. Viewing the Leaderboard

Check out the leaderboard to see the top players. Navigate to the "Leaderboard" page from the navigation bar.

5. Creating a Game

To create a new game, click on "Create Game" and follow the instructions to set up your game.

6. Joining a Game

Join an existing game by clicking on "Join Game" and entering the game code provided by the host.

7. Playing the Game

Once in the game, guess the secret code by entering four unique digits. Feedback will be provided after each guess.

8. Understanding the Game Mechanics

Learn how the game works, including the rules and strategies to improve your chances of winning.
